title: Week In Review: Afghanistan War Ends, Obama's Veto Threat, State GOP Priorities
teaser: Join us for the first Week in Review of 2015! John Munson and his guests discuss major issues in Wisconsin and national politics, including the end of U.S. combat in Afghanistan , veto threats from President Obama , and state Republican priorities for the upcoming session .
